reviews.review: A good ending to the franchise.

I would go into detail but it just felt like a standard sci-fi movie. This doesn't star wars. It will get a high audience review because it is fun, and has many flashing lights, but this isn't a movie you think about. This is an objectively bad movie for 2 hours and has redeeming qualities in the last 30 minutes. The 30 minutes are some of the best of new star wars but then again, that's not saying much.

2nd worst movie IMO. Only ahead of A New Hope. Just watch Mandalorian.
Satisfying into the saga couldn't have done it better
Entertaining but not life changing. It times things together and has some fun throwbacks and new characters.

I liked the film, I got a lot of feelings while watching it. I just thought J.J Abrams did I really good job with what he can. The movie got me entertain. Yeah, there are more things that I would like to put and to take out, but it was fun.  I would probably go watch it for a second time.
I absolutely loved this movie! This was clearly a film made for the fans and not for the critics and I appreciated every second of it!! Perfect ending to the saga!

The Rise of Skywalker is everything The Last Jedi is not, a true Star Wars movie. Unlike Rian Johnson, JJ Abrams crafted a movie for the fans, not the "professional" movie critics. Rise of Skywalker subtlety rejects The Last Jedi and is a welcomed return to the true spirit of Star Wars and a fitting conclusion to a 42 years story arch.

O Filme totalmente sem conexão... deram um hype enorme para Rey que chegou a ser forçado, o Palpatino está vivo fez parecer que os jedi anteriores insignificante.. a trama de romance forçada e bizarra.... resulmão filme com o roteiro mau feito e desconexo

The Killing that started in the last Jedi in unforgivable, here is the final stoke. No chance to develop the knights of Ren subplot, Knights of Ren had no lightsabers. And they never really shine. Suddenly Leia was trained as a Jedi, give me a break. You could have brought Mara skywalker if you wanted to portrait a badass female protagonist. The only Light is thr turn of Ben to the light side again.....at least leave it alive.
